<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog | Data & AI Insights</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #4da6ff;
            --bg: #0a0b10;
            --card-bg: #161b22;
            --text-main: #ffffff;
            --text-dim: #a1a1a1;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* NAVBAR */
        .navbar {
            padding: 20px 8%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: rgba(10, 11, 16, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--primary);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 25px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.3s;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* HEADER */
        .blog-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0f172a, #0a0b10);
        }

        .blog-header h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: var(--text-dim);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* BLOG GRID */
        .blog-container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .article {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .article:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }

        .article-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .article-content {
            padding: 25px;
        }

        .article h2 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .article p, .article li {
            color: var(--text-dim);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .article ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        /* SPECIAL QUOTE SECTION */
        .quote-container {
            grid-column: 1 / -1; /* Makes it full width in the grid */
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #1e293b, #0f172a);
            padding: 60px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            border: 1px dashed var(--primary);
        }

        .quote {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: white;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .navbar { padding: 15px 5%; }
            .blog-container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="navbar">
    <div class="logo">DATA & AI</div>
    <nav>
        <a href="index.html">Home</a>
        <a href="about.html">About</a>
        <a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="blog-header">
    <h1>Insights & Innovations</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
        Exploring the frontier of Data Science and Artificial Intelligence.
    </p>
</section>

<main class="blog-container">

    <article class="article">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550751827-4bd374c3f58b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Cyber Technology" class="article-img">
        <div class="article-content">
            <h2>L'Avantage Décisionnel</h2>
            <p>La vraie valeur réside dans l’exploitation intelligente des volumes massifs de données collectées.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Anticiper les tendances</li>
                <li>Optimiser les performances</li>
                <li>Réduire les risques stratégiques</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </article>

    <article class="article">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Marketing Data" class="article-img">
        <div class="article-content">
            <h2>IA & Marketing Digital</h2>
            <p>L’IA transforme le marketing moderne grâce aux recommandations personnalisées et à l'analyse comportementale en temps réel.</p>
        </div>
    </article>

    <article class="article">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580894732230-2826363aae58?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Coding Skills" class="article-img">
        <div class="article-content">
            <h2>Compétences 2026</h2>
            <p>Les outils indispensables pour rester compétitif sur le marché de la data cette année :</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Power BI & SQL</li>
                <li>Python & Machine Learning</li>
                <li>Advanced Excel</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </article>

    <div class="quote-container">
        <div class="quote">
            “La donnée seule ne vaut rien. Sa valeur naît lorsqu’elle guide une décision.”
        </div>
    </div>

</main>

</body>
</html>
